<div class="layui-form toolbar" style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;">
<form class="layui-form layui-form-pane" onclick="return false;">
    <table class="layui-table">
        <colgroup><col width="150"><col></colgroup>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>媒介名称 *</td>
                <td>
                    <div class="layui-input-inline">
                        <input type="text" name="name" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" value="{[if .Data]}{[.Data.Name]}{[end]}" placeholder="媒介名称">
                    </div>
                    <br/>
                    <p class="layui-font-12">给当前媒介填写一个容易识别的名称。</p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td>媒介类型 *</td>
                <td>
                    <div class="layui-input-inline">
                        <select name="media_type" lay-verify="required" lay-search lay-filter="media">
                            <option value="">[选择媒介类型]</option>
                            <option value="telegram" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.MediaType "telegram" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>Telegram</option>
                            <option value="email" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.MediaType "email" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>邮件</option>
                            <option value="webhook" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.MediaType "webhook" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>WebHook</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <br/>
                    <p class="layui-font-12">通过HTTP请求发送通知。</p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <div id="id_telegram">
                <tr class="id_telegram bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>机器人Token *</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-input-line">
                            <input type="text" name="token" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="请输入Token" value="{[if .Data]}{[.Data.GetTelegramParams.Token]}{[end]}">
                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12">创建机器人的时候可以获得，类似于 123456:AAAA-BBBB ，可以向 @BotFather 发送 /newbot 指令创建新的机器人。</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_telegram bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>接收人标识</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-input-line">
                            <input type="text" name="send_id" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="" value="{[if .Data]}{[.Data.GetTelegramParams.SendID]}{[end]}">
                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12">群或用户的Chat ID,通常是一个数字,可以通过和@get_id_bot[/my_id]建立对话并发送任意消息获得。</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_telegram bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>代理服务</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-inline">
                            <div class="layui-input-inline" style="float: left;">
                                <select name="telegram_proxy_scheme" lay-verify="required" lay-search lay-filter="telegram_proxy_scheme">
                                    <option value="socks5" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.GetTelegramParams.TelegramProxyScheme "socks5" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>socks5://</option>
                                    <option value="https" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.GetTelegramParams.TelegramProxyScheme "https" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>https://</option>
                                    <option value="http" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.GetTelegramParams.TelegramProxyScheme "http" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>http://</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="layui-input-inline" style="float: left;">
                                <input type="text" name="telegram_proxy_value" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="" value="{[if .Data]}{[.Data.GetTelegramParams.TelegramProxyValue]}{[end]}">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12">可选项，仅当API节点所在服务器无法直接连接Telegram API时填写；测试是否能够连接Telegram API的方法： 
curl https://api.telegram.org 出现2XX、3XX、4XX之类提示时说明能够直接连接；如果你设置了代理，请使用 
curl -x "你的代理服务地址" https://api.telegram.org 来测试你的代理是否可用。</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_telegram bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>启用当前Telegram监听</td>
                    <td>
                        <input type="checkbox" name="telegram_listen_enable"
                        {[if .Data]}{[if .Data.GetTelegramParams.TelegramListenEnable]}checked{[end]}
                        {[else]}checked
                        {[end]}>

                        <p class="layui-font-12">开启后，可根据不同的策略，返回不同的响应</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_telegram bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>Telegram监听策略</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-inline">
                            <div class="layui-input-inline" style="float: left;">
                                <select name="telegram_listen_strategy" lay-verify="required" lay-search lay-filter="telegram_listen_strategy">
                                    <option value="none" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.GetTelegramParams.TelegramListenStrategy "none" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>无</option>
                                    <option value="default" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.GetTelegramParams.TelegramListenStrategy "default" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>默认</option>
                                    <option value="append" {[if .Data]}{[if eq .Data.GetTelegramParams.TelegramListenStrategy "append" ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>追加模式</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12"></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_telegram bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>Telegram监听/关联监控分组</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-inline">
                            <div class="layui-input-inline" style="float: left;">
                                <select name="relate_monitor_group_id" lay-verify="required" lay-search lay-filter="relate_monitor_group_id">
                                    <option value="0">无</option>
                                    {[range $g := .groups]}
                                    <option value="{[$g.ID]}" {[if $.Data]}{[if eq $.Data.GetTelegramParams.RelateMonitorGroupID $g.ID ]}selected{[end]}{[end]}>{[$g.Name]}</option>
                                    {[end]}
                                </select>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12"></p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </div>

            <div id="id_webhook">
                <tr class="id_webhook bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>URL *</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-input-line">
                            <input type="text" name="webhook_url" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="http://" value="{[if .Data.GetWebhookParams]}{[.Data.GetWebhookParams.Url]}{[end]}">
                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12">可以在URL中使用 ${MessageUser} 、 ${MessageSubject} 和 ${MessageBody} 来代表接收人标识、标题和内容。</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_webhook bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>请求方法 *</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-input-inline">
                            <select name="webhook_method" lay-verify="required" lay-search>
                                <option value="get" {[if eq .Data.GetWebhookParams.Method "get" ]}selected{[end]}>GET</option>
                                <option value="post" {[if eq .Data.GetWebhookParams.Method "post" ]}selected{[end]}>POST</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </div>

            <div id="id_email">
                <tr class="id_email bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>SMTP *</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-input-line">
                            <input type="text" name="email_smtp" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="类似于 smtp.example.com:465" value="{[if .Data.GetEmailParams]}{[.Data.GetEmailParams.Smtp]}{[end]}">
                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12">只支持SSL（或TLS）连接，端口通常为：465或587。</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_email bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>账号 *</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-input-line">
                            <input type="text" name="email_username" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="类似于 xxx@example.com" value="{[if .Data.GetEmailParams]}{[.Data.GetEmailParams.Username]}{[end]}">
                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12">邮箱账号，比如 123456@qq.com。</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_email bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>密码 *</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-input-line">
                            <input type="password" name="email_password" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="" value="{[if .Data.GetEmailParams]}{[.Data.GetEmailParams.Password]}{[end]}">
                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12">账号对应的密码或者授权码（比如QQ邮箱就需要授权码）。</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr class="id_email bls" style="display:none;">
                    <td>发送者Email</td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="layui-input-line">
                            <input type="text" name="email_from" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="类似于 xxx@example.com" value="{[if .Data.GetEmailParams]}{[.Data.GetEmailParams.From]}{[end]}">
                        </div>
                        <p class="layui-font-12">默认和账号一致</p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </div>

            <tr>
                <td>发送频率 <br/>（次/分钟）</td>
                <td>
                    <div>
                        <div class="layui-inline">
                            <div class="layui-input-inline">
                                <input style="width: 60px;" type="number" name="count" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" value="{[if .Data.GetRate]}{[.Data.GetRate.Count]}{[else]}1000{[end]}" placeholder="">
                            </div>
                            <label class="layui-form-label" style="width: 50px;float: right;">次</label>
                        </div>
                        <span>/</span>
                        <div class="layui-inline">
                            <div class="layui-input-inline">
                                <input style="width: 60px;" type="number" name="minutes" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" value="{[if .Data.GetRate]}{[.Data.GetRate.Minutes]}{[else]}1{[end]}" placeholder="">
                            </div>
                            <label class="layui-form-label" style="width: 70px;float: right;">分钟</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="layui-font-12">用来限制此媒介的发送频率，防止短时间内消息数量过载。</p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td>忽略相似消息周期</td>
                <td>
                    <div class="layui-inline">
                        <div class="layui-input-inline">
                            <input type="text" name="hash_life" autocomplete="off" class="layui-input" placeholder="" value="{[if .Data]}{[.Data.HashLife]}{[else]}60{[end]}">
                        </div>
                        <label class="layui-form-label" style="float: right;">秒</label>
                    </div>
                    <br/>
                    <p class="layui-font-12">可以在这个时间内忽略相似消息，防止短时间内消息数量过载。默认60秒。</p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td>备注</td>
                <td><textarea id="editor2" name="mark" class="layui-textarea" style="min-height:100px;" placeholder="">{[if .Data]}{[.Data.Mark]}{[end]}</textarea></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td>启用当前媒介</td>
                <td>
                    <input type="checkbox" name="status"
                    {[if .Data]}{[if .Data.Status]}checked{[end]}
                    {[else]}checked
                    {[end]}> 
                </td>
            </tr>


            <tr>
                <td colspan="2" >
                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{[if .Data]}{[.Data.ID]}{[end]}">
                    <button class="layui-btn" lay-filter="submit_recipients" lay-submit>保存</button>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</form>
</div>